      "description": "Hey there! You've gotta see this beauty in person\u2014it's in absolutely stunning, mint condition! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been truly loved and meticulously maintained, this is the one for you. Drop me a message if you want to take it for a spin!",
