    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-quality E46 M3, showcasing the pinnacle of the S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six. This specimen features a meticulously maintained dual-VANOS system and a crisp ZF 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis is exceptional, with a verified crack-free rear subframe and factory-spec bushings that preserve the original kinematic precision. Performance is sharpened by the variable M differential lock and high-pressure individual throttle bodies, delivering instantaneous throttle response. The paint depth is consistent with factory standards, showing zero orange peel or oxidation, while the undercarriage remains dry and free of corrosion. A true turn-key example for the collector who demands mechanical perfection and historical authenticity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
