    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-quality 2002 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Carbon Black Metallic over a Cinnamon Nappa leather interior. This vehicle is in breathtaking, showroom condition, having been preserved in a climate-controlled environment its entire life. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining its deep, glass-like factory finish with no swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. The 19-inch forged M Double Spoke wheels are pristine, wrapped in fresh Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires. Inside, the cabin remains in a 'time capsule' state; the leather is supple and matte, the original BMW scent is still present, and there is zero wear on the seat bolsters or steering wheel. All trim pieces are free of scratches, and every pixel on the instrument cluster and head unit is intact. Mechanically, this M3 is peerless. It features a fully documented service history from day one, including the proactive completion of the 'Big Three' E46 requirements: the rear subframe has been reinforced, the VANOS system has been overhauled, and the rod bearings have been replaced with high-performance components. The engine bay is meticulously clean, and the undercarriage is as spotless as the top side. This is a rare opportunity to own an uncompromising, investment-grade icon of German engineering.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
