      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total dream. This car has been pampered since day one\u2014always garaged, meticulously cleaned, and it still looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! You won't find a single blemish or issue here; it's truly in flawless condition and ready for its next adventure. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been incredibly well-loved and looks brand new, you've found it! Drop me a message if you're interested!",
