      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E92 M3, featuring the legendary S65 naturally aspirated 4.0L V8 with its signature 8,400 RPM redline. This specimen boasts impeccable mechanical integrity, with proactive rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service documented. The chassis retains its factory-spec rigidity, complemented by a flawlessly functioning Electronic Damper Control (EDC) system. Power is routed through a precise 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock, ensuring optimal corner-exit traction. The bodywork is free of any paint depth inconsistencies or swirling, while the cabin maintains its original matte leather finish and tactile switchgear integrity. This is a superlative, turn-key example for the collector prioritizing mechanical purity and atmospheric performance.",
